name: Mackenzie US Large Cap Equity Index ETF (CAD-Hedged)
longDescription: The ETF seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible. The Fund before fees and expenses, the performance of the Solactive US Large Cap Hedged to CAD Index, or any successor thereto.
fulldescription: The ETF seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible. The Fund before fees and expenses, the performance of the Solactive US Large Cap Hedged to CAD Index, or any successor thereto. It invests directly or indirectly in US equity securities, with its foreign currency exposure hedged back to the Canadian dollar
fullAddress: 180 Queen Street West, Ontario M5V 3K1, Toronto, ON, CA
